com.upsight.android.persistence.annotation

Annotation Type UpsightStorableType


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value={TYPE,METHOD})
public @interface UpsightStorableType
    Annotates classes or methods to be persisted in the UpsightDataStore. When in a class this annotation must define a unique type to be used in the data store. When used in a method, this method must match the format below: public String [method-name](); // Returns the type for which this class represents.
    See Also:
    UpsightDataStore, UpsightDataStore.store(Object), UpsightDataStore.remove(Object)

      The type name.
